description: Meeting new pledge Lance Weber for the first time, chapter prefect Aspen has to admit he's less than impressed. When Lance suggests he may have persuaded Aspen's brother's with a little oral consideration, Aspen becomes livid, telling Lance that he gets first crack at any new crack, and he marches Lance upstairs directly. Once there, his opinion of Lance changes immediately, as the new pledge shows off the skills that earned him such strong consideration. Aspen has to admit, he may not have got there first, but it was worth the wait, and when Lance fucks the cum out of him and coats him with his own load, Aspen agrees with his brothers that Lance's shortcomings are nothing compared to his thick, long ones.Enjoy!
title: Alpha Gets It First
